DTLN_v2.0

This project is an engineering rewrite of the DTLN denoising and AEC
tooling. It keeps the core DTLN processing idea while reorganizing the project
into a maintainable package with configuration, data validation, tests,
benchmarks, and compatibility shims.

Upstream reference:

- breizhn/DTLN: https://github.com/breizhn/DTLN
- DTLN paper: Dual-Signal Transformation LSTM Network for Real-Time Noise
  Suppression, Proc. Interspeech 2020.

